  interactButton: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueCanvas: {fileID: 0}
  dialogueText: {fileID: 0}
  conversation:
  - text: Ma'am cafeteria lady! There seems to be an issue.
  - text: What is it, little girl?
  - text: I received the wrong change! I need more!
  - text: What?! That can't be right. Its from the machine!
  - text: No, I recomputed everything! I'm sure it's an error.
  - text: Hmm, how can we check... OH! Detective! I didn't see you there. I was too
      focused.
  - text: Would you mind checking the receipt if it computed correctly?
  - text: Where is it though, little girl?
  - text: I left the receipt on top of a table, by the chair closest to the trash
      can near the poster.
  - text: I see. Please help us, detective!
